# easy inispec to use to develop the gtkconfig interface
SECTION Machine
    DESCRIPTION Information about the Machine to be used with the compiler
PROPERTY name
    TYPE string
    DESCRIPTION Give me a name for the machine, pick whatever you fancy
PROPERTY endianness
    TYPE string
    DEFAULT little
    VALUES little, big
    DESCRIPTION Endianness of the input file
PROPERTY device
    TYPE path
    DESCRIPTION Path to found the device file, use the 'red.dat' file
PROPERTY changebits
    TYPE bool
    DEFAULT false
    DESCRIPTION Activate this to change the device bits
PROPERTY bits
    TYPE int
    DEPENDS_ON Machine.changebits
    DESCRIPTION Bit size of the system to simulate
    DESCRIPTION the behaviour of the system if you have changed the
    DESCRIPTION bit type of the processor. You can use 16 or 32.
